column1: In case of problem, please report to:
<DESCRIPTION>Black hole masses of z~1.4 AGNs from SXDS (Nobuta+, 2012)</DESCRIPTION>
<DESCRIPTION>Broad-line fitting results and black hole  masses for the broad-line AGNs</DESCRIPTION>
<!-- Broad-line fitting results and black hole masses for the broad-line AGNs {\em (tables 3 and 4)} -->
<DESCRIPTION>[10/1242] Source identification number; <[UWS2008] NNNN> in Simbad</DESCRIPTION>
<!-- [10/1242] Source identification number; \dicS{[UWS2008] NNNN} in Simbad -->
<FIELD name="z" ucd="src.redshift" datatype="float" width="6" precision="3"><!-- ucd="REDSHIFT_HC" -->
<FIELD name="logLXh" ucd="phys.luminosity;em.X-ray" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="[10-7W]"><!-- ucd="PHYS_LUMINOSITY_X" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Log of 2-10 keV hard X-ray luminosity; erg/s</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="W(Mg)" ucd="spect.line.width" datatype="int" width="5" unit="km/s"><!-- ucd="SPECT_LINE_FWHM" -->
<DESCRIPTION>? FWHM of broad MgII emission line [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="e_W(Mg)" ucd="stat.error" datatype="short" width="4" unit="km/s"><!-- ucd="ERROR" -->
<DESCRIPTION>? Uncertainty in W(Mg) [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="W(Ha)" ucd="spect.line.width" datatype="short" width="5" unit="km/s"><!-- ucd="SPECT_LINE_FWHM" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[1492/11056]? FWHM of broad H{alpha} emission line [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="e_W(Ha)" ucd="stat.error" datatype="short" width="3" unit="km/s"><!-- ucd="ERROR" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[3/456]? Uncertainty in HaWidth [NULL integer written as an empty string]</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="logLo" ucd="phys.luminosity" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="[10-7W]"><!-- ucd="SPECT_LUMINOSITY" -->
<FIELD name="R-i" ucd="phot.color;em.opt.R;em.opt.I" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="mag"><!-- ucd="PHOT_CI_R-I" -->
<FIELD name="logM" ucd="phys.mass" datatype="float" width="4" precision="1" unit="[Msun]"><!-- ucd="PHYS_MASS_MISC" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[6.6/9.8] Log of the black hole mass</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="logL" ucd="phys.luminosity" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="[10-7W]"><!-- ucd="PHOT_BOL_LUMINOSITY" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[43/48.1] Log of the bolometric luminosity; in erg/s (3)</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="logWEd" ucd="phys.luminosity;arith.ratio" datatype="float" width="5" precision="2" unit="[-]"><!-- ucd="PHYS_LUMINOSITY_RATIO" -->
<DESCRIPTION>[-2.5/0.2] Log ratio of observed and Eddington-limited accretion rates</DESCRIPTION>
<!-- ask the {\bf\fg{FireBrick}Simbad} data-base about this object -->
<FIELD name="_RA" ucd="pos.eq.ra;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="9" precision="5" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_RA_MAIN" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Positions from SXDS III. (Ueda et al. 2008, Cat. J/ApJS/179/124) (right ascension part)</DESCRIPTION>
<FIELD name="_DE" ucd="pos.eq.dec;meta.main" ref="J2000" datatype="double" width="9" precision="5" unit="deg"><!-- ucd="POS_EQ_DEC_MAIN" -->
<DESCRIPTION>Positions from SXDS III. (Ueda et al. 2008, Cat. J/ApJS/179/124) (declination part)</DESCRIPTION>
